re than $\\frac14 - \\varepsilon$ fraction of (adversarial) errors in the input\nstream $\\mathsf{enc}(x)$.\n</summary>\n    <author>\n      <name>Meghal Gupta</name>\n    </author>\n    <author>\n      <name>Rachel Yun Zhang</name>\n    </author>\n    <link href=\"http://arxiv.org/abs/2307.07087v1\" rel=\"alternate\" type=\"text/html\"/>\n    <link title=\"pdf\" href=\"http://arxiv.org/pdf/2307.07087v1\" rel=\"related\" type=\"application/pdf\"/>\n    <arxiv:primary_category xmlns:arxiv=\"http://arxiv.org/schemas/atom\" term=\"cs.DS\" scheme=\"http://arxiv.org/schemas/atom\"/>\n    <category term=\"cs.DS\" scheme=\"http://arxiv.org/schemas/atom\"/>\n  </entry>\n</feed>\n"}